        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 9. Phyllodoce brasiliensis sp. nov. A, anterior end in dorsal view; B, anterior end, lateral view showing lateral sensorial cavities with a black arrow; C, lateral view of everted proboscis showing: (C1) short and robust antennae; (C2) proximal area of proboscis with rows of papillae; (C3) distal part with tubercles; (C4) terminal ring of probocis. A–C, Holotype. Scale bars: A–C, 1.0 mm; B, 0.7 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4496826/files/figure.png" .

